{"tid":850421,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【街霸重臨】代理與地監職員起衝突 有人被一拳KO","createTime":"2018-10-06T13:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T14:10:12.000Z","uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"beaa297a4c77cd5abf4608598fd413988764dc29","tid":850421,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"2018年10月06日<br />\n<br />\n【街霸重臨】代理與地監職員起衝突 有人被一拳KO<br />\n<br />\n【更新地監局回應】<br />\n<br />\n近期二手市場冰封，<span style=\"color: red;\">大批代理無單開要轉戰一手新盤搶客</span>。<br />\n<br />\n位於太子始創中心，九建油塘海傲灣售樓處門外，有人目睹，現場地產代理與現場監察的地監局職員起衝突，居然一拳將該名地監局人員揮低，令他受傷倒地。其後警員到場，該名打人者被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n地監局回應指，有關事件已交警方依法處理，而監管局亦會跟進個案，任何被證實於執業期間涉及暴力案件而被定罪的地產代理，除了會留有案底之外，亦會被監管局撤銷牌照，而有關人士所屬的地產代理公司，亦有可能因沒有妥善管理其員工操守而被處分。監管局已聯絡有關樓盤的發展商作出跟進，改善有關銷售處的秩序安排，而本局人員會繼續堅守於一手住宅物業銷售處進行巡查工作，並會適當地增加人手安排。監管局譴責任何不法使用暴力的行為，並強調絕不容忍任何害群之馬，嚴重損害地產代理業界之形象。<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳寶恩 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181006/large/1538819382_3163.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181006%2Flarge%2F1538819382_3163.jpg&h=f9cb96ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181006/large/1538818839_a671.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181006%2Flarge%2F1538818839_a671.jpg&h=b6f64969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181006/58764462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58764462&d=l%2Bx78FohU5h7b8dWRBrBCMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=bbe99c79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181006%2F58764462&h=feacc1a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181006/58764462</a>"},{"pid":"01e637ff70c0e910a53816b454f905c5fac277cf","tid":850421,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗，正"},{"pid":"3465f6ff3f5f2c329ee7f33648ba3036435af096","tid":850421,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e637ff70c0e910a53816b454f905c5fac277cf","tid":850421,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗，正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"監管局職員同代理係兩回事"},{"pid":"c0aef6b7f88a84d234c733a6fdfe9f024974b0fb","tid":850421,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"3465f6ff3f5f2c329ee7f33648ba3036435af096","tid":850421,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e637ff70c0e910a53816b454f905c5fac277cf","tid":850421,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗，正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"監管局職員同代理係兩回事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"我夠知啦，唔係狗咩？"},{"pid":"4a5daadae07f0c5e5d79e9f098e4e5e00fd35998","tid":850421,"uid":110113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c0aef6b7f88a84d234c733a6fdfe9f024974b0fb","tid":850421,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"3465f6ff3f5f2c329ee7f33648ba3036435af096","tid":850421,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e637ff70c0e910a53816b454f905c5fac277cf","tid":850421,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗，正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"監管局職員同代理係兩回事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"我夠知啦，唔係狗咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T13:36:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af05eca83e998e0ab8f6eaa49e82e30a5e47ddf","tid":850421,"uid":147367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"